speaker.name: Leandro Nunes
speaker.biography: I'm a software engineer, currently working on compilation tools for machine learning workloads and contributing to the Apache TVM Compiler Stack as a PMC member and committer. In the academic background, I hold a M.S. degree in Microelectronics and a B.S. degree in Computer Science.
